thread.title: CORRECT-(OFFICIAL)-Wynn Macau Says Q4 ‍Net Profit $179.2 Mln ​

author: Reuters Editorial
title: CORRECT-(OFFICIAL)-Wynn Macau Says Q4 ‍Net Profit $179.2 Mln ​
text:
(Corrects net profit figure in headline and bullet to $179.2 million after company revises it from $187.2 million)
Jan 22 (Reuters) - Wynn Macau Ltd:
* QTRLY ‍NET PROFIT ATTRIBUTABLE $179.2 MILLION VERSUS $46.6 MILLION ​
* QTRLY TOTAL OPERATING REVENUE $1.31 BILLION VERSUS $917.1 MILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
